{"about_the_game":"<i>It's not about the destination, it's about the journey.</i><br>Heading Out is an immersive driving game meets visual novel passionately inspired by cult classic road movies.<br>Escape your fears by taking off down American highways on an emotional trip of discovery.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640630/extras/01_gameplay.gif?t=1737489986\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong></h2><strong>Your Adventure - What's your motivation?</strong><br>The fears, dreams, ambitions and choices of your driver pave the road ahead so each run is a unique combination of races, chases, hazards and colorful characters.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640630/extras/02_comix_art-gif_000_delay-0.03s.gif?t=1737489986\" /><br><br><strong>Your Path - Will you, or won't you?</strong><br>Each strategic decision impacts a variety of systems including who you meet along the way, what radio hosts say about you, fuel consumption, car condition and wanted level.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640630/extras/04_map-gif_000_delay-0.03s.gif?t=1737489986\" /><br><br><strong>Your Legend - When and where does it end?</strong><br>An eclectic Americana soundtrack backs each road trip playthrough as your experience expands across the unpredictable western frontier.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640630/extras/03_cinematic.gif?t=1737489986\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"I Want to Break Free","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1640630/057991ea2b24a46c1746d04bfc9435955e8ce6a6.jpg"},{"name":"We Are the Champions","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1640630/d16f438c9b7325511fbea678da8a5cd9e3d69b78.jpg"},{"name":"Never Catch Me","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1640630/a7899ad01e19dcb6ff0ae33ef6ccbfb2b8028b7d.jpg"},{"name":"Take It Easy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1640630/8259284bc5e9efcf2b93b03ec4b830805f202417.jpg"},{"name":"Local Hero","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1640630/3354b5f6526206964cb3ab362fca58b5e9962f14.jpg"},{"name":"Nailed it","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1640630/7e957aa5de56c84d42b944f7ce8eb900baf8e817.jpg"},{"name":"Fast Car / Slow Traffic","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1640630/9187cdca599e44f5df188d47ac9a4b9e55e6471d.jpg"},{"name":"Paranoid","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1640630/d9676ee44b3352278be20999b4fe3090ffe67ac3.jpg"},{"name":"On the Road Again","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1640630/4068c93c3fd9542d3fe7542241cfb38660c1795b.jpg"},{"name":"Another Day in Paradise","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1640630/c235456c092d7cec8ec4d6cbeea79378947ec9be.jpg"}],"total":55},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640630/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737489986","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640630/page.bg.jpg?t=1737489986","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640630/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737489986","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640630/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737489986","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Family Sharing","i